title: Stunning One Bedroom Live Life on Main Up To Four Weeks Free
posting_body: ['Welcome to Surrey On Main', 'Find your serenity within at Surrey on Main.', 'Caught between urban and residential Bellevue, Surrey on Main is a haven for those who live here.', 'Color and white space balance for inspiration and relaxation simultaneously.', 'History hidden in plain sight rewards curiosity while everyday elegance creates a sanctuary in our busy, bustling world.', 'Inside each home, warm, wood-style plank flooring juxtaposes tones of gray and black in the quartz countertops, black metal accents, and dark pendant lights.', 'A canvas of clean lines and warm light, the space is waiting to become your own.', 'Surrey on Main’s community spaces are plush and polished, but you’re still free to put your feet up after a long walk.', 'After all, this is your sanctuary.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 113', 'OR Text', '113', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 720 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Kitchen', '- Oven', '- Air Conditioning', 'Community Amenities', '- Community Lounge', '- Dog Wash', '- Package Room', '- Rooftop Patio', '- Fitness Center', '- Bike Wash', '- Car Chargers', '- 24 Hour Availability', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats and Dogs Allowed', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Thursday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Surrey on Main', '10777 Main St , Bellevue, WA, 98004', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', '16wRtnCrX6qN']
